Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:02.97,5-normal,signs,0,0,0,,{\fs80\bord0\shad0\c&H14141F&\pos(960,430)}Penguasa Wilayah Terpelosok dan Gadis Bertanduk {\c&HA05604&}Biru
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.09,0:00:16.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wilayahku sendiri, isinya cuma rumput.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.77,0:00:30.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebulan berlalu sejak aku diseret\Nnaik kereta kuda dari ibu kota.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.28,0:00:36.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, sudah sampai.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.85,0:00:38.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Turun!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.68,0:00:46.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wilayah ini cocok sekali untuk yatim piatu\Nyang mendadak naik kasta.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.57,0:00:49.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini peta batas wilayahmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.84,0:00:53.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan daftar penganugerahan\Ndari Yang Mulia Raja.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.37,0:00:59.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padang rumput ini bernama Nezrose.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.20,0:01:04.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai hari ini, namamu Dias Nezrose.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.45,0:01:15.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi ini wilayahku...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.94,0:01:18.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raja memberiku tanah ini
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,sebagai hadiah atas jasaku di medan perang.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.25,0:01:24.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak terlalu paham,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.14,0:01:27.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi katanya tugas Penguasa Wilayah itu\Ntinggal di wilayahnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.27,0:01:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,melindungi rakyat,\Ndan memungut pajak untuk Raja.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.65,0:01:42.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untung ada air bersih di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.62,0:01:46.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu perang, aku cuma minum air lumpur.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.80,0:01:50.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah sejauh ini jalan,\Ntapi tak ketemu siapa-siapa.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.17,0:01:53.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan sebatang pohon pun tak ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.97,0:01:54.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,sekarang aku paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.80,0:02:00.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wilayahku isinya cuma rumput.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.22,0:02:04.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waduh!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak enak.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan coba semampuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.17,0:02:14.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dua hari lagi masih buntu,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.60,0:02:18.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,lebih baik aku tinggalkan padang rumput ini\Nsebelum mati konyol.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa ke desa terdekat,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.19,0:02:24.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,cari kerja yang berguna untuk orang lain\Ndemi bertahan hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.48,0:02:27.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setidaknya aku masih\Nmemegang wasiat orang tuaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.14,0:02:32.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.51,0:02:34.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bangun!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.34,0:02:37.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bangun!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang apa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namaku Dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti yang kau lihat,\Naku cuma tidur di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa tidur di tempat begini?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena tak ada tempat lain untuk tidur.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.02,0:02:59.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ini bodoh, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.03,0:03:04.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak bisa kusangkal,\Nsampai setua ini aku tak berpendidikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus, kau sendiri...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk apa kau menginjakkan kaki\Ndi padang rumput ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.51,0:03:09.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa tujuanmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku disuruh tinggal di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau ditanya tujuan, untuk saat ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku cuma belum mau mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei. Tunggu, tunggu dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.11,0:03:23.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jawab yang benar!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku serius...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.11,0:03:32.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin memegang wasiat ayah dan ibuku,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,yaitu jadi orang yang berguna\Nbagi orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.40,0:03:39.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin melindungi yang lemah.\NItulah tujuanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau tak berbohong saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.82,0:03:48.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa apanya?\NMemangnya aku punya alasan berbohong?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ini musuh atau sekutuku?\NYang mana?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.58,0:03:57.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana bisa kujawab untuk orang\Nyang baru pertama kutemui.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak bisakah kalau kita netral saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.02,0:04:02.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak! Jawab dengan tegas!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.57,0:04:05.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa dia marah-marah?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.31,0:04:07.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.47,0:04:11.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini wilayahku, berarti dia rakyatku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.98,0:04:16.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pasti kesal karena aku\Nsebagai Penguasa Wilayah belum tegas
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,menyatakan diri di pihaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.71,0:04:23.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ada di pihakmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa pun musuhnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,kupastikan kau aman bersamaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cahayanya terang sekali...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.00,0:04:33.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kok bisa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cahaya apa itu tadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa? Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudahlah, diam dan ikuti aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mbeq.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Desa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal kemarin aku sudah\Nkeliling sejauh itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,kok bisa terlewat?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus temui Kepala Suku.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.97,0:05:08.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tumben kau bawa orang luar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.08,0:05:12.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna, sama sekali tak ada warna merah?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada, Nek. Semuanya biru.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat kutanya dia berpihak padaku,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,cahayanya biru terang\Ndan dia menjawab "ya".
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menarik juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria biru, siapa namamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, ya. Namaku Dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.65,0:05:28.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.89,0:05:35.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bilang berpihak pada Alna,\Ntapi mau berpihak padaku juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua orang di sini rakyatku,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.89,0:05:42.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan aku dititahkan Raja\Njadi Penguasa Wilayah kalian...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan gegabah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia belum selesai bicara.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa ceritakan semuanya dari awal,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.71,0:05:58.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,bagaimana Raja bisa menitahkan itu padamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari awal, semuanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.25,0:06:07.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak aku mulai bisa mengingat,\Nkedua orang tuaku masih hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.88,0:06:12.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuku bilang aku harus cari kerja\Nyang berguna bagi orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.45,0:06:16.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayahku bilang aku harus jadi\Npria pelindung yang lemah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu wasiat mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.97,0:06:25.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat aku berusia 10 tahun,\Nmereka wafat karena wabah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kumpulkan anak-anak\Nyatim piatu senasib.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami bersihkan jalanan kota\Ndemi upah harian,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.91,0:06:36.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,memburu monster lemah demi uang saku,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.91,0:06:40.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,pokoknya kami berjuang keras\Nsesuai wasiat orang tuaku,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.31,0:06:43.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,agar tak membuat mereka malu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat usiaku 15 tahun, perang pecah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.85,0:06:51.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasukan musuh merangsek cepat\Nsampai kota sebelah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.37,0:06:56.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi melindungi teman-temanku,\Naku daftar jadi prajurit sukarela.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.18,0:07:01.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Awalnya tak kusadari,\Ntapi rupanya aku berbakat bertarung,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.10,0:07:04.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,katanya aku terus mencetak\Nprestasi besar di medan perang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dua puluh tahun berlalu, perang pun usai.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.94,0:07:12.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raja hadiahkan tanah ini padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.14,0:07:17.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memang Penguasa Wilayah\Nyang sungguh ingin melindungi rakyatnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,sekarang aku paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.08,0:07:26.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku ingin tanya,\Nbagaimana kalau kami bukan rakyatmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masih mau berpihak pada kami?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.63,0:07:32.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai tetangga\Ndi padang rumput yang sama,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.57,0:07:35.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau kalian butuh bantuan,\Naku pasti turun tangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.31,0:07:37.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa kita tetap bisa jadi sekutu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kenapa tanya begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah siapa pun yang tinggal di sini\Notomatis jadi rakyat...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm? Lo?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru sadar, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.22,0:07:55.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami bukan rakyatmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malahan,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.49,0:07:59.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami musuh Rajamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.71,0:08:06.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah bertahun-tahun,\Nkami berperang melawan negaramu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.94,0:08:12.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi mungkin kami bukan musuhmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memancarkan warna biru.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biru yang sangat langka.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.00,0:08:22.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Nkita pasti bisa hidup berdampingan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.25,0:08:27.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, angkat kepalamu dan dengarkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.91,0:08:33.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namaku Moll, Kepala Suku Oni.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami sudah lama berseteru
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.43,0:08:41.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan negaramu, memperebutkan\Nkekuasaan atas padang rumput ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.05,0:08:45.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lima puluh tahun lalu,\Nkami kalah dalam perang besar,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.51,0:08:49.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan Suku Oni pun melarikan diri dari sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kalian lari,\Nkenapa sekarang tinggal di sini lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.42,0:08:56.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan menyimpan mana di tanduk ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.62,0:08:59.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami bisa pakai berbagai sihir.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salah satunya adalah...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sihir Penyembunyian.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.00,0:09:10.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kekuatan ini,\Nkami bisa menyembunyikan seluruh desa
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menghilangkan hawa keberadaan kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.28,0:09:17.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pantas saja aku tak menemukannya kemarin.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.11,0:09:21.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi apa boleh diberitahukan padaku,\Norang Kerajaan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.54,0:09:25.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau bukan warna biru,\Ntakkan kuceritakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami punya sihir bernama Penilai Jiwa.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.37,0:09:32.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Merah menandakan bahaya dan niat jahat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.22,0:09:35.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Putih berarti tak berbahaya\Ndan tak berniat jahat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.40,0:09:39.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biru berarti orang itu membawa kebahagiaan\Ndan berkah bagi kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.89,0:09:44.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berbohong sedikit saja,\Nwarnanya akan keruh berubah kemerahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi warnamu tak berubah sama sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, masuk akal.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru kali ini kulihat orang sejujur ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.45,0:09:56.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,hidup sampai setua ini\Ndemi memegang teguh wasiat orang tua.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku baru saja dipuji?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari tadi kupuji kau.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.88,0:10:08.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, aku akan dukung kau\Njadi Penguasa Wilayah yang hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.82,0:10:13.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami memang tak bisa jadi rakyatmu,\Ntapi kami beri rumah,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.82,0:10:16.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,makanan, dan sedikit hewan ternak.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.54,0:10:20.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai gantinya,\Nrahasiakan desa ini dari siapa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.74,0:10:22.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Termasuk dari Rajamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.71,0:10:26.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pribadi tak masalah dengan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama kalian tak bersinggungan\Ndengan kerajaan,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,silakan tinggal di padang rumput ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.31,0:10:36.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai pengurus sementaramu,\Nkupinjamkan Alna.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.05,0:10:40.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tinggallah dengannya,\Nbiarkan dia mengajarimu cara hidup di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang membawanya kemari.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanggung jawab sampai akhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengerti?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.80,0:11:11.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru mulai dirakit,\Ntahu-tahu sudah hampir jadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.10,0:11:15.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau ada krisis yang tak bisa dihindari\Nmeski dengan Sihir Penyembunyian,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,rumah ini bisa dibongkar\Nagar kita bisa kabur bersamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.35,0:11:19.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah fungsi Yurt ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, jadi namanya Yurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.65,0:11:23.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.62,0:11:31.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti makanan dan Mbeq akan dikirim.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.74,0:11:34.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna, Mbeq itu apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hewan ternak.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.91,0:11:38.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari obrolan tadi harusnya kau paham, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.22,0:11:44.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kita biakkan, jumlahnya bertambah,\Npenghasilanmu stabil.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.51,0:11:49.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuajari cara merawatnya\Nsetelah mereka tiba. Simak baik-baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mo-Mohon bantuannya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau bisa, ajari juga aku\Ncara menambah rakyat...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana aku tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.17,0:12:04.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk apa menambah rakyat\Nkalau kondisinya begini?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yurt dan makanan saja cuma cukup buatmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.82,0:12:10.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau orang bertambah,\Nujung-ujungnya kelaparan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penguasa Wilayah bodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.51,0:12:16.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bubuk Matabi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau ditabur, binatang buas\Nyang mencium baunya akan mendekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.97,0:12:26.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Buru mereka,\Nbawa daging dan kulitnya ke desa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa ditukar uang, bahkan Yurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menarik juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau berburu, aku jagonya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.17,0:12:36.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Toh tak perlu berpikir rumit!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.42,0:12:41.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekitar sini harusnya cukup.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi tak sempat tanya takarannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.86,0:12:46.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudahlah, tabur semuanya saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang tinggal tunggu hewannya datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.62,0:12:55.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kira-kira butuh berapa ekor\Nuntuk ditukar satu Yurt, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.02,0:13:01.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebanyak ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.57,0:13:05.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau berhasil kuburu semua,\Nbisa-bisa dapat beberapa Yurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.65,0:13:11.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gaya bertarungku adalah...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.31,0:13:17.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,mengayunkan kapak perang\Nmengandalkan insting dan tenaga murni.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.15,0:13:19.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, sesederhana itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.66,0:13:33.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekitar setengahnya kabur,\Ntapi hari ini cukup segini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.11,0:13:38.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus, ini bagaimana cara mengangkutnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk sementara, kubawa pulang satu ekor,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.55,0:13:51.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi tadi aku cuma mengamuk\Ntanpa berpikir cara membawanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti Alna bakal merendahkanku lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.68,0:13:59.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tatapan sedinginnya itu\Nlumayan menusuk mental.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh juga kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.91,0:14:08.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.28,0:14:13.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru pertama berburu\Nsudah tumbangkan Kurogi!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kejantananmu tangguh juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi namanya Kurogi, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.97,0:14:22.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya bukan cuma ini,\Nkuburu separuh kawanannya,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi tak sanggup membawanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa ajari aku cara...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Separuh? Memangnya berapa banyak?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.42,0:14:31.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa sekitar 30-40 ekor...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.68,0:14:34.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Banyak sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ini?\NPenilaianku langsung berubah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.77,0:14:41.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat juga,\Nlangsung tunjukkan ketangguhanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.80,0:14:46.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar sekali! Baru kali ini\Nkulihat kejantanan sehebat ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.08,0:14:48.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kupanggil para pemuda desa!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebelum matahari terbenam,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.20,0:14:55.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita harus angkut Kurogi hasil buruan Dias!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sebut namaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memang sungguh kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kejantanan yang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.20,0:15:07.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Kejantanan" itu maksudnya apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tolok ukur nilai pria di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.05,0:15:13.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah pekerja keras, tangguh,\Natau bisa diandalkan,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.42,0:15:16.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,semua kami sebut kejantanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.77,0:15:21.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu sebabnya suasana hati Alna\Ntiba-tiba membaik?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna kan sudah dewasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhadapan dengan kejantanan sehebat itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,sudah pasti hatinya berbunga-bunga.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.85,0:15:32.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa pria dengan kejantanan hebat\Nitu populer?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.31,0:15:36.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di luar faktor lain seperti wajah tampan\Natau obrolan nyambung...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong kosong macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.54,0:15:41.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memangnya tampang dan obrolan\Nbisa bikin kenyang?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.75,0:15:46.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menikahi pria tidak jantan\Ncuma bikin anak-anak kelaparan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.06,0:15:52.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagi wanita, selain kejantanan,\Ntak ada nilainya sama sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.17,0:15:55.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata nilai di sini\Nberbeda jauh dengan Kerajaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.97,0:16:00.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau mau nikahi Alna,\Nkarena dia cantik dan rajin,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,maharnya bakal lebih mahal, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ti-Tidak, tidak!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.05,0:16:05.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sama sekali tak berniat sejauh itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.94,0:16:07.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak usah khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.97,0:16:11.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertanduk atau tidak,\Ntetap bisa punya anak, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.74,0:16:16.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan! Sama sekali bukan itu\Nyang kukhawatirkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pagi, Dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sarapan baru saja matang.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.64,0:16:37.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, ini enak sekali, Alna!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.85,0:16:43.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Be-Begitukah? Padahal aku masaknya\Ntak repot-repot amat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, Dias...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.17,0:16:53.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.90,0:16:56.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana rencana berburu hari ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.11,0:16:58.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tangkapan kemarin masih kurang?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.41,0:17:02.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mau kumpulkan orang di sini,\Nkita butuh sumur dan toilet.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.60,0:17:06.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk sewa perajin desa,\Nbayarannya masih kurang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.51,0:17:09.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku akan berburu Kurogi lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.21,0:17:13.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan, kalau hewannya itu-itu saja,\Nmereka bosan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau incar monster hari ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.68,0:17:18.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Monster, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dagingnya penuh miasma beracun,\Ntak bisa dimakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.68,0:17:26.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi cakar, tanduk, dan batu sihirnya\Nlaku dijual mahal.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu kau sering berburu monster, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.68,0:17:33.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, tapi apa di sini ada monster?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedikit, tapi pasti ada kalau dicari.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa pakai sihir pelacak monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.31,0:17:41.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau ikut denganku,\Nurusannya cepat selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.34,0:17:44.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berbahaya kalau lawannya monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cukup beri tahu tempatnya, aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.66,0:17:50.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berburu yang membosankan pun\Npasti seru kalau kita berdua!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.25,0:17:59.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Bulu Mbeq berharga bukan karena dagingnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.81,0:18:02.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,makanya penting disisir..."\NBegitu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enak rasanya, Francis?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.71,0:18:08.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Giliranmu, Francoise.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Dias!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.25,0:18:16.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kubawakan daging kering\Ndan selimut pesananmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk Yurt, tolong tunggu sebentar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.49,0:18:22.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pekerjaan perajin kami sedang menumpuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong sampaikan\Naku tak buru-buru, santai saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata kalau punya wibawa dan kejantanan,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita juga dihormati kaum pria, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dias,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku sudah siap.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Riasannya beda...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana bilangnya, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mohon bantuannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.97,0:18:49.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.80,0:18:53.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah titipkan perawatan Mbeq\Npada pemuda desa.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makanya, hari ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.78,0:18:59.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau boleh habiskan waktu\Nseharian penuh denganku, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Ayo cepat pergi berburu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.28,0:19:11.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa monsternya sering muncul\Ndi sekitar sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.79,0:19:14.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan soal melacak monster padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.74,0:19:18.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak cuma jago rumah tangga,\Ntapi juga ahli sihir!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.30,0:19:20.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengandalkanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.05,0:19:31.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yujinsis, Clasp, Intoshize, Intorigi,\NIntoare, Nuinto...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.81,0:19:40.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hize, Bo, Into, Shiezuvon,\NToredisuta, Kurasuto, Angeata...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketemu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.00,0:19:46.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Monsternya lumayan besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Besar, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kuperiksa sendirian dulu ke sana,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.91,0:19:52.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau tunggu di sini saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.94,0:19:57.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau lupa?\NAku bisa Sihir Penyembunyian.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.00,0:20:01.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau lawannya di luar kemampuan,\Nkita bisa bersembunyi lalu kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.08,0:20:07.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah. Kalau tak membahayakanmu,\Nayo bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu kan...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kura-kura?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Earth Dragon...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa ada di pelosok begini?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi bukan kura-kura, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.14,0:20:23.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, coba kupukul sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.85,0:20:27.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan lakukan hal bodoh!\NItu Naga, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bersembunyilah, Alna.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keras sekali! Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.62,0:20:45.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata dia bisa menutup celahnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lari mumpung masih sempat, Dias!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.89,0:20:51.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadapi Earth Dragon sendirian itu ceroboh!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.89,0:20:55.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal kabur, nanti saja\Nsetelah kucoba semampuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.36,0:21:03.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau satu pukulan tak mempan,\Nkuulangi dua kali, tiga kali...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah gaya bertarungku!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah mulai rusak, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.08,0:21:25.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perbaiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.51,0:21:29.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa...?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.94,0:21:30.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.31,0:21:34.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wajar kaget kalau baru pertama lihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.70,0:21:37.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapak perang ini kudapat setelah
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.64,0:21:41.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,mengalahkan pria dari negara tetangga\Nyang dijuluki Shogun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.74,0:21:45.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bentuknya menyerupai singa,\Nluar biasa kokoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.90,0:21:49.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau cuma retak kecil,\Ndibiarkan saja bisa sembuh sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.02,0:21:53.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kalau kufokuskan\Ndan perintah "perbaiki", langsung pulih.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, ayo kita lanjutkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.20,0:22:10.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kacau juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.25,0:22:13.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah dihajar bertubi-tubi pun\Ncangkangnya tak hancur.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Miasma milik Earth Dragon...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.62,0:22:21.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski dari jarak sejauh ini,\Nracunnya perlahan menggerogotiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.08,0:22:23.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau kedinginan?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.68,0:22:26.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya sudah waktunya kita pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesal rasanya tak bisa robohkan\Nkura-kura begini,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.74,0:22:33.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi waktunya akhiri dengan ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.57,0:22:36.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pecah!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.22,0:22:49.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata dia bisa menyerang balik begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.26,0:22:53.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.34,0:23:04.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Monster itu mengincar Alna?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.02,0:23:08.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan aku, tapi dirinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.03,0:23:09.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takkan kubiarkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.78,0:23:11.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah berjanji.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa pun musuh yang menghadang,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.49,0:23:15.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.74,0:23:17.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.66,0:23:19.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,melindungimu!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.71,0:23:26.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.54,0:23:32.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Alna?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.97,0:23:34.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau menikah...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.45,0:23:35.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.94,0:23:39.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau menikah denganmu!
